node.text: ⚠️KARMAGAWA FUNDRAISER FOR AFGHANISTAN UPDATE, PLEASE WATCH/SHARE/DONATE!⚠️Thank you everyone who has shared our posts abut Afghanistan and donated to our new @karmagawa fundraiser as we’ve now raised $150,000+ in just over a week to help the Afghan people during this URGENT crisis. I’m proud to announce that I’ll be personally matching ALL donations dollar for dollar with my recent trading profits so now we have $300,000+ raised to help these refugees with food, water, medical treatment and temporary shelter too, 100% of which will be donated to charities like @partnersrelief @savethechildren and other charities on the ground in/around Afghanistan to help as many refugees as possible. My cofounder @badboi and I are BIG believers in transparency so stay tuned to see the details of all our donations on Karmagawa.org just like how we show the $6+ million we’ve already donated to 70+ charities worldwide…thank you again for your support and please keep sharing our posts and donating whatever you can as EVERY share and donation helps these families in their time of deep need RIGHT NOW!

node.text: ⚠️AMAZING KITTEN RESCUE!⚠️ During our recent trip to Greece, my friends @everchanginghorizon and @jess.wandering rescued the cutest little kitten that was abandoned on a cliffside and I was honored to be able to help too after getting introduced to @zawf.zante.gr an incredible animal rescue charity that desperately needed more funding to help save more animals! I donated 1,000 euros to them on the spot, but we have also created a @karmagawa fundraiser with the goal of raising $25,000 to get them a full on shelter and veterinarian on their staff because there are SO many more animals in Zakynthos that need URGENT help so please donate what you can, share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too and let’s all work together to raise the $25k ZAWF needs to help more animals in need! Sadly, this little kitten didn’t make it and that’s why we MUST get these poor animals more help faster in the future…see my stories for the link to the @karmagawa Facebook fundraiser and ALL donations great and small are most appreciated! #helpanimals #savethekitties #zakynthos #animalrescue

node.text: ⚠️SHARE TO HELP SAVE OUR PLANET BEFORE IT’S TOO LATE⚠️Repost from @karmagawa We humans are destroying our environment and wildlife in so many different ways as this sad but accurate cartoon replaces the roles of humans and animals in today’s society to show us all a different perspective and if there’s any hope of saving our planet and too many endangered species before it’s too late, then we MUST confront these issues RIGHT NOW and that starts with education and spreading awareness to everyone! So, watch this video a few times as it covers many of the methods in which we’re destroying the only planet we all have and really think about its message because it’s 100% true and sadly it’s future generations of humans and animals that will suffer the greatest consequences of our irresponsible behavior, especially if we do nothing and allow all of this destruction to continue. We MUST work together and fight for our planet and our wildlife so please share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers in the comments who need to see it and share it with their followers too — it’s not too late for us to change our ways, all our wildlife and our planet deserves it! Great video by Steve Cutts and music by Kina #saveourplanet #climatechange #globalwarming #endanimalcruelty #karmagawa

node.title: How To Stay Safe And Profit From The Coronavirus Pandemic

node.text: I'm getting SO many questions right now so I stayed up late last night to make this video that answers a lot about what I see happening right now...stay safe, err on the side of caution when it comes to your health, don't worry if anyone says you're overreacting -- when there's a global pandemic happening, it's okay to be overly-safe, it's actually encouraged! With all that said, there's TONS of trading opportunities if you're prepared on these coronavirus stocks, for example, today is one of the worst days in stock market history and I've made a rather safe and low-risk $3,000+...and I've been averaging $1,000-$2,000 in profits per day lately while some of my top students like Tim Grittani, Marck Croock and Jack Kellogg have all been making upwards of $10,000, $20,000 or even $100,000+ in a day so study up and stay indoors more. Now, not only has the NBA canceled their season, the MLB and NHL too so you have no sports to distract you from your studies...make the best out of the next few weeks and study up by watching my now 6,300+ video lessons and 1,000+ archived webinars, you can get educated while you stay safe too! #coronavirus #stockmarket #stateofthejewnion

node.text: I’ve lived a crazy life and been fortunate enough to be able to fulfill all my childhood dreams and more. My mission these days is all about helping others live their dream lives too, teaching them to become millionaires through stock trading along with my @karmagawa charity’s mission to build schools all over the world and also helping the environment through my @savethereef project...and I’m only able to do all this while traveling nonstop because I’ve focused on what I love and put my entire being into every project I take on. Too many depressed people message me every day because they’re busy building other people’s dreams...please stop doing that! Maximize this extraordinary time in history and utilize all the new tools and technology that is revolutionizing education like never before! Thank you @iamjoelbrown for this great video, sorry for making so many jokes throughout the interview :) #throwbackthursday #buildyourowndreams #jewsinthejungle

node.text: Repost from @karmagawa Here’s why we are SO proud for Karmagawa to support animal rescue centers like @animalaid_india all over the world as they help so many animals in need! Please share this video with your followers and tag people, influencers and celebrities who need to see it as four small puppies came close to losing their lives in a horrendous accident when they stumbled into spilled tar in a garbage pile, but thanks to the hard work of some kind-hearted individuals these puppies were saved! When the first one wandered in and got stuck in the tar, she must have cried so much that the others came to see what was the matter, and they too got glued down by the awful tar. We knew they had a mother, but we couldn't find her until the day after their rescue and the hours-long process of removing the tar with oil and dish soap. These poor puppies were dazed with confusion, pain, fear and frustration, and two were so completely covered that all they could move was their eyes. But by the time Mommy arrived, they were freed from the poisonous grip of the tar and ready for the comfort of her love! We ALL must do what we can to help animals whenever possible…share this story with your followers and let’s inspire everyone to make this a better planet for humans and animals alike! #helpanimals #kindnessmatters #karmagawa

node.title: Saving Puppies From A Tragic Accident

node.text: This is why I LOVE animals so much!!! Repost from @karmagawa  A baby elephant was stuck upside down in a gutter, while a pride of lions were closing in…but elephants are truly amazing creatures so watch what happens and please share this video with your followers and tag someone who needs to see it as videos like this help show how incredible animals are so WE MUST DO A BETTER JOB PROTECTING THEM! Roughly 100 elephants die every day and at the current rate they will be extinct in the next decade or so…we need to get the word out before it’s too late as the empathy of elephants never ceases to amaze us! Great video @newsnercom #savetheelephants #animalsrock #karmagawa

node.title: Baby Elephant Is Stuck Upside Down

node.text: It’s been an amazing few weeks for me in Europe celebrating with several of my top students who have each crossed $1 million in trading profits, but the highlight here in Positano, Italy was definitely our amazing boat trip thanks to the one and only @leanneperice and @buckingham_lloyds a company I can’t speak highly enough about as not only have they committed to being more sustainable (which many more companies should do) they’ve also made this a trip to remember for all of us! And since it’s my students’ first time here in Italy, they’ve been in FULL ON vacation mode while I’m still trading/teaching nonstop and also coordinating several new @karmagawa and @savethereef projects so I couldn’t put my laptop down…even while aboard this boat :) Some people tell me to “stop working and take a day off”, but if you love what you do, like I’m so fortunate to do, you never “work” a day in your life…truly. Please congratulate my hardworking students turned master traders @jackkellogg @mari_hincapiee @kyle_cwilliams @matthewvmonaco @rolandwolf86 @mikehuddie and thanks again to @buckingham_lloyds for this badass boat trip! #proudteacher #ilovemyjob #celebration #positano

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND JOIN US IN PRAYING FOR LOUISIANA!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa Hurricane Ida is causing devastation and power outages in Louisiana after its Category 4 landfall with life-threatening storm surge, catastrophic winds and dangerous rainfall flooding. Ida has tied two other hurricanes for the strongest landfall on record in the state of Louisiana based on maximum wind speeds as Laura had 150-mph winds when it tracked into southwest Louisiana last year and the only other hurricane with winds that high was all the way back in 1856. So far, more than 400,000 customers without power in Louisiana and Energy Louisiana said some of its customers could be without power for weeks. "Everyone should listen to the instructions from local and state officials just how dangerous this is, and take it seriously. It's not just the coast, it's not just New Orleans, it's north as well," President Joe Biden said Sunday at the Federal Emergency Management Agency headquarters in Washington, DC. Please join us in praying for all those in the path of this dangerous hurricane and share this post/tag people who need to see it because we must warn EVERYONE to stay safe and take this storm seriously as Louisiana needs all our support and prayers right now! #prayforlouisiana #hurricane #staysafeeveryone #ida #louisiana #hurricaneida #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️KARMAGAWA FUNDRAISER FOR AFGHANISTAN UPDATE, PLEASE WATCH/SHARE/DONATE!⚠️Thank you everyone who has shared our posts abut Afghanistan and donated to our new @karmagawa fundraiser as we’ve now raised $150,000+ in just over a week to help the Afghan people during this URGENT crisis. I’m proud to announce that I’ll be personally matching ALL donations dollar for dollar with my recent trading profits so now we have $300,000+ raised to help these refugees with food, water, medical treatment and temporary shelter too, 100% of which will be donated to charities like @partnersrelief @savethechildren and other charities on the ground in/around Afghanistan to help as many refugees as possible. My cofounder @badboi and I are BIG believers in transparency so stay tuned to see the details of all our donations on Karmagawa.org just like how we show the $6+ million we’ve already donated to 70+ charities worldwide…thank you again for your support and please keep sharing our posts and donating whatever you can as EVERY share and donation helps these families in their time of deep need RIGHT NOW!

⚠️GRAPHIC IMAGE WARNING: PLEASE SHARE AND DONATE TO OUR NEW FUNDRAISER TO HELP THE AFGHAN PEOPLE!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa These devastating videos show the cruelty/brutality of the Taliban because their way of life involves violence, pain, suffering and murder. As difficult as it is, please watch these videos to understand why so many Afghans are so desperate to escape before it’s too late in a few days time. The first video is of a young woman being publicly flogged in front of hundreds of men and now the Taliban say that women should not go to work for their own safety, contradicting earlier press conferences where they claimed they would be more tolerant towards women this time around. This happened the same day that the World Bank halted funding in Afghanistan, citing concerns about the safety of women, and within hours of the UN calling for a "transparent and prompt investigation" into reports of human rights abuses since the Taliban takeover. The second video is of an Australian citizen who was beaten by the Taliban while trying to reach an evacuation flight at the Kabul airport — and the video ends abruptly with a gunshot…THIS IS NOT OKAY! Please share this post on your story/with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers and news media who must share it too as we must all use our social platforms to make EVERYONE aware of why we must help as many people, especially women and children, escape from the cruel Taliban before the August 31st deadline. Please share this post RIGHT NOW, donate to our fundraiser where 100% of funds will be donated to helping the Afghan people with food, water, medial treatment and shelter in their time of need and join us in praying for all the people and families in Afghanistan!  #prayforkabul #prayforafghanistan #helpkabul #afghantaliban #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS: PLEASE SHARE AND DONATE TO OUR FUNDRAISER TO HELP THE AFGHAN PEOPLE!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa Soldiers from several countries have stepped in to take care of the babies/children of families hoping to escape Afghanistan before the August 31st deadline for the withdrawal of international troops from the troubled country. Sadly, now its being reported that at least 20 people have died in the past week in and around the Kabul airport during the chaotic evacuation effort after the Taliban took over the Afghan capital last week and more deaths are expected in the coming days so we must ALL work together to save as many people as possible before it’s to late. Please keep sharing our posts about this crisis with your followers and tagging people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and also share this to get more international help and please keep donating to our fundraiser as we’re very proud that between the @karmagawa and @savethereef communities, we’ve now raised $130,000+ in the past week alone, 100% of which will be donated to charities like @partnersrelief and @savethechildren which are both now in the planning stages on how to help as many families as possible in Afghanistan! While we recognize this is a small dollar amount for such a big problem, we hope to raise much more in the coming days as EVERY donation great and small will go towards providing food, water, medical treatment and shelter for the Afghan people and EVERY LIFE MATTERS so please keep praying, donating and sharing and we’ll update our rescue efforts along the way as these children and families need all our support RIGHT NOW! #helpafghanistan #saveafghanistan #savethechildern #kabulafghanistan #childrendeservebetter #prayforafghanistan #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC IMAGES/SAD BREAKING NEWS: PLEASE SHARE AND DONATE TO OUR NEW FUNDRAISER TO HELP THE AFGHAN PEOPLE!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa The crisis at the Kabul airport in Afghanistan is getting worse as new videos show mothers resorting to passing their babies over barbed wire to soldiers in a vain attempt to get them out of the country. Westerners and visa holders trying to get to their flights say they are unable to get to the gates because of the crowd of up to 50,000 desperate locals who are gathering at the gates. While US and UK troops have said that firing warning shots is a last resort, the Taliban have been filmed today shooting from the hip just yards away from women and children, and whacking people with the butts of their rifles. Sadly, the chaos outside the airport appears to be growing by the day and is causing dangerous stampedes in which several people have already been killed this week, including a 14-year-old girl. WE MUST GET THESE PEOPLE MORE HELP! Please join us in praying for all the people and families now stuck in Afghanistan, donate to our new Karmagawa fundraiser where 100% of the funds will be donated to @partnersrelief @savethechildren and other charities on the ground in this area and share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see/share this too as we must make EVERYONE aware of what’s happening here to get them help RIGHT NOW! The International community must not look away so please use your social platform for good and share this now to get help for the Afghan people! #prayforkabul #prayforafghanistan #helpkabul #afghantaliban #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️PLEASE SHARE AND DONATE TO OUR NEW FUNDRAISER TO HELP AFGHANISTAN RIGHT NOW!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa We’ve launched a new Karmagawa fundraiser to help those fleeing the cruel Taliban in Afghanistan and this post should make everyone understand better why people are so desperate to escape RIGHT NOW! Please swipe over and look closely at every picture and video and share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and news media who need to see and share it too, and also donate if you can as we MUST work together to help the Afghan people in their darkest hour. EVERY share and EVERY donation great and small matters right now as it’s just been one day since the Taliban took control and already there are already stories coming out about their cruelty towards women in particular. In northern Afghanistan, The Taliban demanded a mother of four in a small village cook food for up to 15 fighters. "My mother told them, 'I am poor, how can I cook for you?'" her daughter said. "The Taliban started beating her. My mother collapsed and they hit her with their guns — AK47s." The woman died from the beating.⁠ The Taliban denied the killing, but their words are contradicted by witnesses and local officials who confirmed the death of a 45-year-old women whose home was also burned. This is just one of many stories because to Afghanistan's women, the Taliban represents the sudden and devastating loss of rights gained over 20 years, the right to work, study, move and even live in peace, that they fear will never be regained. WE MUST HELP THE AFGHAN PEOPLE RIGHT NOW and that’s why we’ve started this new fundraiser and have already begun planning with several charities on the ground there so 100% of the money we raise will be donated to helping Afghans escape from such cruelty…use your social platform for good and please share this and donate too! Info from @middleeastmatters @cnn @theafghan #helpafghanistan #afghanistan #saveafghanistan #karmagawa

May be an image of text that says 'MIDDLE EAST MATTERS A lifetime of rape & sexual servitude awaits unmarried girls in Afghanistan following the Taliban's control over the region. Jihadist commanders have forced the imams in the areas they have seized to bring them a list of unmarried girls for their soldiers to marry. "They view them as qhanimat or 'spoils of war' to be divided up among the victors," Daily Mail reports. The fighters have been going door-to-door to 'claim their prizes'-young girls that will be subjected to a lifetime of sexual servitude. Sources: WSJ, The National, Dailymail'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Timothy Sykes on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Nearly 400,000 were forced from their homes since the beginning of the year, joining 2.9 million Afghans already internally displaced across the country at the end of 2020. ·80 percent of internally displaced are women and children. In June alone, 109,000 people were internally displaced within the country. Thousands of people are rushing from rural areas to the capital Kabul and other urban centers in search of shelter. Around 15,000 internally displaced persons have arrived in Kabul from other provinces. Most of them are sleeping in the open, in parks and public spaces.'.

Photo by Timothy Sykes on August 17, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people sitting and text that says 'The Taliban knocked on her door 3 times. The fourth time, they killed her VHUNIYUR CNN'.

node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC WARNING/SAD BREAKING NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND LET’S PRAY FOR AN GET HELP HERE!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa There’s chaos at Hamid Karzai International Airport in Kabul as Afghans try to flee the Taliban who just took control of Afghanistan, pouring into the capital, Kabul, and meeting little resistance. President Ashraf Ghani fled the country as the Taliban took over the presidential palace and the government collapsed and now gunfire and fear has now gripped the city, with tens of thousands of people trying to escape and witnesses say at least 5 people have died so far following desperate scenes at Kabul airport. Tragic video shows heavy gunfire, people storming the gates and scaling the 10- to 20-foot concrete walls to get onto the airfield with some even trying to cling onto the planes as they took off, with several people falling midair. With all scheduled flights now suspended, many foreigners and Afghans are now stranded as the militants' return to rule brings an end to almost 20 years of a US-led coalition's presence in the country. Please join us in praying for all the people and families now stuck in Afghanistan and share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too as we must make EVERYONE aware of what’s happening here to get them help RIGHT NOW! The International community must not look away so please use your social platform for good and share this now to get help for these people! #prayforkabul #prayforafghanistan #helpkabul #afghantaliban #karmagawa

node.text: It’s actually pretty sad the kind of narrow-minded messages I’m getting after our recent international @karmagawa fundraisers for hard-hit countries like Greece, Turkey, Algeria and now Haiti as too many people mistakenly believe we should donate ONLY to issues affecting the United States. We already have several US charity projects along with new upcoming projects in New York, Connecticut, Florida, California, Colorado and Texas to name a few, but we also recognize that we’re ALL ON THE SAME PLANET TOGETHER and the devastating wildfires in Europe and now the earthquake in Haiti requires us to spread awareness and raise as much funds as possible to help them in their time of need. We REALLY must leave narrow-mindedness behind and unite as one people to make this a planet we can ALL be proud of! #weareone #dontbenarrowminded #cmonpeople #karmagawa #letsunite

node.text: ⚠️SAD NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND LET’S HELP THOSE IN NEED RIGHT NOW!⚠️ I am SO proud of the @karmagawa and @savethereef communities for now raising $60,000+ in less than a week to help the hard hit communities of Greece and Turkey and I have 2 announcements to help even more, 1.) we’re adding Algeria to the list of countries to donate to after 65 people there were just killed by wildfires and 2.) we at @karmagawa will be matching the $60,000+ already raised dollar-for-dollar thanks to my recent trading profits and 100% of the profits from our charity apparel designed by my Karmagawa co-founder @badboi so that we’ll be donating at least $120,000+ to help as there are sadly hundreds of wildfires burning in these countries right now! Our fundraiser is ongoing so please keep donating and sharing posts about this crisis to help spread awareness as these countries need all the help they can get right now since tens of thousands of people have already lost everything, dozens have died along with countless animals, there are now mass evacuations and entire communities have burned to the ground so we are raising funds to help those affected with food, water, shelter and medical treatment in their time of need...we appreciate ALL donations great and small and even if you can't donate, please share this fundraiser as every last share also helps! #givingback #helpthoseinneed #helpgreece #helpturkey #helpalgeria #wildfire

node.text: I’ve been trading like absolute crap the past few days so I think it’s time I change it up with a new haircut by one of my favorite hairstylists @tomoca13 who flew in all the way from Japan! Whatcha think, do you like my haircut with a view here in the Italian countryside and more importantly, will this new look help my trading? Or should I stop being such a degenerate trader during this choppy August and just size my positions down and be more patient like ALL my top students have done (I’m a little bit slower than them LOL)

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND LET’S HELP GREECE AND TURKEY!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa We are calling on EVERYONE to help Greece and Turkey in their time of need because while these countries are being ravaged by wildfires, they are sadly ill-equipped to put them all out and save people/animals in time so the international community MUST HELP THEM RIGHT NOW! In the past 3 days, dozens of towns and villages in Greece have been evacuated as a protracted heatwave and strengthening winds fueled more than 150 wildfires and scientists say the destruction in just the last 72 hours exceeds 50% of the average area burnt in previous years! In Turkey, 8 people have died, tens of thousands have been evacuated and thousands of animals have perished and despite these wildfires burning 7x more land this year than any year in decades, this country has NO firefighting planes, so we must send them help! You can help by using your social media platform to spread awareness about this by sharing this post with your followers and tagging people, celebrities, influencers and news media who need to see and share this too and and donate to our new Karmagawa fundraiser where 100% of funds raised will go towards to providing medical treatment, food, water and shelter for all the people and animals affected by these devastating fires. We MUST all come to the aid of Greece and Turkey right now as this sadly record-breaking heatwave is forecast to continue for several days more so please share this post, donate and let’s all work together to help these hard-hit countries RIGHT NOW! #helpgreece #helpturkey #prayforturkey #prayforgreece #wildfire #letshelpeachother #karmagawa
